- 'get_legal_moves' to get a UCI formatted list of available moves
- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

get_legal_moves

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Proxy (to Player_Black):

h8g7,g8f8,g8e8,g8d8,g8c8,g8b8,g8g7,g8g6,g8g5,g8g4,g8g3,g8g2,g8g1,a8f8,a8e8,a8d8,a8c8,a8b8,e6c8,e6f7,e6d7,e6f5,e6d5,e6g4,e6h3,b5c7,b5d6,b5d4,b5c3,b5a3,c4d6,c4b6,c4e5,c4a5,c4a3,c4d2,c4b2,h7h6,b7b6,a7a6,e3e2,h7h5,a7a5

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

make_move g8g2

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Proxy (to Player_Black):

Move made, switching player

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- 'get_legal_moves' to get a UCI formatted list of available moves
- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

get_legal_moves

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Proxy (to Player_Black):

f6g7,f6f7,f6e7,f6g6,f6e6,f6g5,f6f5,f6e5,b5c7,b5d6,b5d4,b5c3,b5a3,h3c8,h3d7,h3e6,h3f5,h3g4,h3g2,h3f1,f2g4,f2e4,f2d3,f2h1,f2d1,h7h6,a7a6,h7h5,a7a5

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

make_move a7a6

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Proxy (to Player_Black):

Move made, switching player

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

You are a professional chess player and you play as black. Now is your turn to make a move. Before making a move you can pick one of the following actions:
- 'get_legal_moves' to get a UCI formatted list of available moves
- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

make_move b4b3

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Proxy (to Player_Black):

Move made, switching player

- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

get_legal_moves

- 'get_legal_moves' to get a UCI formatted list of available moves
- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

You are a professional chess player and you play as black. Now is your turn to make a move. Before making a move you can pick one of the following actions:
- 'get_legal_moves' to get a UCI formatted list of available moves
- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

get_legal_moves

- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

You are a professional chess player and you play as black. Now is your turn to make a move. Before making a move you can pick one of the following actions:
- 'get_legal_moves' to get a UCI formatted list of available moves
- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

get_legal_moves

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Proxy (to Player_Black):

g8h8,g8f8,g8g7,g8f7,c5d7,c5e6,c5a6,c5e4,c5a4,c5d3,c5b3,h7h6,b7b6,a7a6,e5e4,h7h5,b7b5,a7a5

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

make_move c5d3

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Proxy (to Player_Black):

Move made, switching player

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

make_move c3b3

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Proxy (to Player_Black):

Move made, switching player

- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

get_legal_moves

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Proxy (to Player_Black):

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

make_move d5d4

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Move made, switching player

You are a professional chess player and you play as black. Now is your turn to make a move. Before making a move you can pick one of the following actions:
- 'get_legal_moves' to get a UCI formatted list of available moves
- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

get_legal_moves

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- 'get_legal_moves' to get a UCI formatted list of available moves
- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

get_legal_moves

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Proxy (to Player_Black):

f6g7,f6f7,f6e7,f6g6,f6e6,f6g5,f6f5,f6e5,c4c6,c4c5,c4h4,c4g4,c4f4,c4e4,c4d4,c4b4,c4a4,c4c3,c4c2,c4c1,c7c6,b7b6,h6h5,a5a4,f2f1q,f2f1r,f2f1b,f2f1n,c7c5,b7b5

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

make_move f6e5

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Proxy (to Player_Black):

Move made, switching player

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

- 'get_legal_moves' to get a UCI formatted list of available moves
- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

get_legal_moves

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Proxy (to Player_Black):

d3g6,d3f5,d3e4,d3c4,d3e2,d3c2,d3f1,d3b1,b3c4,b3b4,b3a4,b3a3,b3b2,b3a2,h7h6,g5g4,b5b4,a5a4,h7h5

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Player_Black (to Proxy):

make_move g5g4

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Proxy (to Player_Black):

Move made, switching player

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
